      <title>晶片零件供應商Siltronic利潤因客戶庫存高而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chip-parts-supplier-siltronics-profit-falls-high-client-inventories-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德國晶片設備供應商世創電子(Siltronic)週四報告稱，第一季度核心利潤下降了27.5%，一周前該公司因客戶庫存仍然很高而大幅削減了年度目標。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chip-parts-supplier-siltronics-profit-falls-high-client-inventories-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:59:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
